<H3> <TI>   Heroin Discovered in Beersheba Prison </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Heroin Discovered in Beersheba Prison </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA3004081194 </F>
<F P=103> TA3004081194 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
BFN 

    [Editorial Report] Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television 
Network in Hebrew at 1700 GMT on 27 April reports that "280 
units of heroin were discovered yesterday in Beersheba prison. 
The authorities also know with certainty about another 50 
incidents in which drugs were smuggled into the prison over the 
past five months." 
  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English at 1000 GMT on 18 April 
reports: "Two Egyptian infiltrators were last night caught 
south of Mitzpe Ramon after a long chase. A kilogram of heroin 
was found in their possession. They also had binoculars, 
clothing, and provisions for a long stay under field conditions." 

</TEXT>

