<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Two Kilos of Heroin Hidden in Broken </F>
Down Car"] 
  [Excerpts] The drug trade has to accept the failure of 
another billion-schilling deal: In a parking lot along the 
southern highway near Graz, a Pole who had hidden 2 kg of pure 
heroin with a black-market value of 8 million schillings in his 
car was arrested. [passage omitted] 
  Andrzej G., 22, from Poland admitted that he was supposed to 
take the drugs from Poland to Italy. His reward: 1,000 German 
marks. It is currently investigated whether he had already made 
"deliveries" along the way before being arrested. 

</TEXT>

