<H3> <TI>   Brazilian Attempting To Smuggle 5 Kg of Cocaine Arrested </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Brazilian Attempting To Smuggle 5 Kg of Cocaine Arrested </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0205084194 Istanbul SABAH in Turkish 24 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> NC0205084194 </F>
<F P=104>  Istanbul SABAH </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Damaris Lisoba Gomes Sardinia, 28, was detained at 
Ataturk Airport in Istanbul for trying to smuggle 5 kg of 
cocaine into Turkey yesterday. Sardinia, who is a citizen of 
Brazil, arrived in Turkey from Spain. The police discovered 5 
kg of cocaine in the pockets of her slacks in her suitcase after 
she passed through immigration control. She was handed over to 
the officials of the Narcotics Department after the police at 
the airport interrogated her. 

</TEXT>

