<F P=100> CENTRAL EURASIA </F>
<F P=101> BELARUS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Representatives of UN Narcotics Control Board Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Representatives of UN Narcotics Control Board Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0405135994 Minsk BELAPAN in Belarusian 1236 GMT 4 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> WS0405135994 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk BELAPAN </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Between 4 and 6 May, representatives of the UN 
International Narcotics Control Board [INCB] will be paying an 
official visit to Belarus. The main goal of the visit is to 
discuss international treaties concerning the fight against 
drugs, cooperation between Belarus and the INCB, technical 
assistance to Belarus in this area, and the development of a 
national mechanism for controlling the production and 
distribution of drugs and psychotropic substances. 
  It is expected that in the course of the visit, the INCB 
representatives will meet with Belarusian Interior Ministry 
leaders and workers from various Interior Ministry departments. 
[passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-67131 </DOCNO>
