BFN 

  [Text] The East Rand narcotics squad made their largest 
dagga [marijuana] haul, valued at 4.5 million rands. The police 
said that the 4.5 tonnes of dagga was discovered on a farm in 
the Grootvlei district near Heidelberg last night. A number of 
people were arrested and will appear on court on Monday. 

