<H3> <TI>   Country Reportedly `World's Biggest Clearing House' for Qat </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Country Reportedly `World's Biggest Clearing House' for Qat </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WD0353A London THE SUNDAY TIMES in English 3 Apr 94 p 
8--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WD0353A </F>
<F P=104>  London THE SUNDAY TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


