<H3> <TI>   MVD Official Cited on Crackdown in Almaty </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    MVD Official Cited on Crackdown in Almaty </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1216A Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA in Russian 11 May 94 
p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1216A </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA </F>
