  [Text] The goal of operation Transit, which was recently 
launched in Sumy Oblast, is to uncover and seize narcotic 
substances transported to the oblast by drug traffickers. 
During the first days of the action, which is being conducted 
by workers of the Interior Ministry, the Border Troops and 
Customs Service have already seized as much as 500 kg of poppy 
