<H3> <TI>     Three Arrested in Anshan City for Heroin Trafficking </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Three Arrested in Anshan City for Heroin Trafficking </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2105062094 Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1000 GMT 20 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2105062094 </F>
<F P=104>  Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A few days ago, Anshan city cracked a serious case 
in the trafficking of narcotics. Informed of a narcotics sale 
that was to take place at the intersection of (Feishichang) Road 
in Tiedong Sanmen, public security cadres and policemen took 
quick action and arrested the criminal (Li Hongxun), a worker of 
Anshan city Beifang (Gongman) Company, on the spot on the 
evening of 17 April. One hundred grams of heroin was seized, 
and another 180 grams of heroin was found at his house. (Sha 
Muqing) and (Guo Xingyan), two criminals involved in this case, 
were also captured. This is the largest drug bust in Anshan 
city to date. 

</TEXT>

