<H3> <TI>   Statistics on Narcotics Users Detailed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Statistics on Narcotics Users Detailed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WD0333A Athens TA NEA in Greek 9 Apr 94 p 13 </F>
<F P=103> 94WD0333A </F>
<F P=104>  Athens TA NEA </F>
<F P=105>  Greek </F>


<TEXT>
