<H3> <TI>   Police Arrest 10 in Operation To Halt Heroin Trafficking </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Police Arrest 10 in Operation To Halt Heroin Trafficking </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1805130594 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1157 GMT 18 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BR1805130594 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
