<H3> <TI>   Controversy Over Plans to Bury Hungarian Nuclear Waste </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Controversy Over Plans to Bury Hungarian Nuclear Waste </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0804202394 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 
1500 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0804202394 </F>
